        "id": 1172779
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-06-08T04:28:50Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "maybe nevermind. It looks like dynamnic initialization time is implementation defined and may be deferred until first use of a global variable. Zero initialization happens at thread creation, but I\u0027m not seeing a way to get dynamic initialization at thread creation.",
      "parentUuid": "c3aff637_106d2e54",
      "revId": "9ab1d6179d0fb0292d44552bdb40a8457b83190c",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
      "unresolved": true
